tileMatrixSetDefinition is the one offered by the service in a different path. Required for custom TMSs and optional to point to an internal repetition of the ones present in the annexes (and in the NA). tieMatrixSetURI is a pointed to the NA (and the annexes). We should push for the NA to return a json representation. Required if the "standard" TMS is used. tileMatrixSet is not intended for OGC API Tiles. mediaType: the media type of the tiles.
